de: Addendum No 4 to the Project Agreement concerning the Grant for the Project KIK-44 "the Programme for enhancing the use of renewable energy sources and improving the quality of air within the natura 2000 areas in the Poviat of Sucha Beskidzka" between Switzerland represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and the Republic of Poland represented by the Ministry of infrastructure and development as the National Coordination UNIT (NCU)  - 14-09-2015 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Polen, vertreten durch das Ministerium für regionale Entwicklung, bezüglich der Förderung erneuerbarer Energiequellen in der Region Poviat Sucha Beskidzka, KIK-44
